<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../public/css/style.css">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@4.12.10/dist/full.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" />
    <style>
        /* Smooth Hero Section Fade-in */
        .hero-content {
            animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(20px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        /* Stylish Button */
        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #ff6f61, #ffcc00);
            border: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.6);
        }

        /* Improved Text Styling */
        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: #ffcc00;
            text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 204, 0, 0.8);
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../includes/navbar') %>

    <div class="hero min-h-screen"
        style="background-image: url(https://www.bhmpics.com/downloads/aesthetic-line-art-black-background/3.06fcf5247475b9e7af44e401cf816fcf.jpg);">
        <div class="hero-overlay bg-opacity-80"></div>
        <div class="hero-content text-neutral-content text-center">
            <div class="max-w-md">
                <h1 class="m-5 font-bold">Welcome to Anzone!</h1>
                <p class="mb-5">
                    We&apos;re thrilled to have you here at Anzone, your go-to resource for inspiration, support, and growth. 
                    Our mission is to help women like you thrive by providing access to self-work tools, essential helpline numbers, 
                    and a vibrant community of stories and experiences.
                    <br><br>
                    Explore our collection of empowering blogs and discover the incredible journeys of women who have transformed their lives. 
                    Whether you&apos;re seeking motivation or looking to share your own story, EmpowerHer is here to support you every step of the way.
                    <br><br>
                    Join our community, find your path, and let&apos;s inspire and uplift each other together. Welcome to a space where your journey 
                    matters and your voice is valued.
                </p>
                <a href="/helpline">
                    <button class="btn btn-primary">Explore More!</button>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <%- include('../includes/footer') %>

    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</body>
</html>